title: Welcome to HAXCamp 2022!
description: Get ready for Camp! We're excited to bring HAXCamp to Penn State on May 9-10, 2022.Looking to get in contact with the HAX family? Connect with us on slack!Also, we'll be using this trello board for ideation during the event.
